Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,FATHER AND SON DRAGONS SET OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or does anyone think\NDai and I will not be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you nuts?!\NThat's the greatest tag team in the world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you willing to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, Hyunckel needs healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you agree with us\Nthat Dark King Ban is a mutual enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll gladly accept your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, go with your father\Nto the Dark Citadel Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, I can go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru, please heal Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Maam, and Crocodine\Nwill take on the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We will set out once you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand, Dino?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief. He's been pouting ever since\Nit was decided that they work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They've just been standing there\Nnot talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we avoided a fight\Nbetween father and son again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And temporary as it may be,\NBaran is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I still don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met him before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but Dai's father seems different\Nfrom what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I do sense overwhelming power from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but he doesn't seem like the violent type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time we fought, it was hardly\Nthe mood for working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He risked his life to reach\Nan understanding with Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,His being incapacitated\Nwas a high price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He always assumes\Nno one will grieve if he ever dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a relief to know\Nhe can't take risks anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, he needs to learn\Nto take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will only be helping you this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Only until our mutual goal of killing\NDark King Ban is accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that's over,\Nwe are destined to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence will only\Ncomplicate things on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing... I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My... My mother... What was she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother... Soara...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And... a kind woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mere presence\Nfilled everyone around her with warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She overflowed with such light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt I will ever\Nlove anyone that deeply...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ever... again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Toberura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there was to be a single exception...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it would be you, Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon father and son are off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they'll pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear the two of them working together
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,may instead awaken an even greater evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Just ignore what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like anyone could ignore what a seer says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru, don't worry!\NWe'll do our best out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we've got not one,\Nbut two Dragon Knights helping us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If we lose, then it wasn't to be.\NOur enemy was stronger than the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point in worrying, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Maam, Big Guy, looks like we're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing the Royal Guard alone\Nwon't be easy, but I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We only need to keep them here\Nwhile Dai and Baran open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Hold down the fort for us, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Hyunckel, Chiu,\Nand the other wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't bother with cliche parting words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We always do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There they go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you slow me down,\NI'll leave you behind without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Nova.\NYou wanted to go with them, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I did. But I already know\NI'm not as strong as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay and help reorganize the backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If it turns out that Dark King Ban\Ncan't be beaten with two Dragon Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's better than doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just do everything we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can I be so selfish?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the one under\Nthe most pressure in this battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}God of Dragons...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}please bless Dai, Popp, and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time for the main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I hope I never have\Nto come to this awful place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the Dark Citadel Gate is open,\Nwe fight Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't leave alive\Nunless we defeat our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's focus on luring\Nthe Hadorra Royal Guard here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. If only we had more help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gomechan?!\N-You followed us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed us to this dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The little guy must not have\Nwanted to be left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've got\Na pretty reliable friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gome,\Nyou've been with us from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick with us to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you noticed, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, Maam's butt\Nlooked bigger than usual, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,POPP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!\NDon't waste your energy fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one fooling around, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you two get married,\NI know who's going to be in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I ever marry such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky. You may quarrel a lot,\Nbut you have a powerful bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats having a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that watching Dai and Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I manage to survive this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll find a wife of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all... go home alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, I hope all goes well with your dad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave things here to us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABRAKE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's the entrance to Ban Palace?\NWhere's the Dark Citadel Gate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to find it quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It won't be easy for Popp\Nand the others fighting alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relax.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This voice... Is that...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm talking to you through telepathy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I figured it would be possible\Nthrough the resonation of our crests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Telepathy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, nothing will start\Nuntil we breach the gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Focus on fulfilling your objective.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The queen looks brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Hyunckel\Nhit them with his attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they can regenerate\Nusing Hadorra's Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! You plan to fight us\Nwith just yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about overconfident!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Watch out\Nor you'll regret underestimating us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where's that damn pointy bishop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get some payback for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fenbren is missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is our emblem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The bishop moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't on Hadorra's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry everybody...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but this target belongs to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, you're not going...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously. To the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds are beyond normal healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be blunt. You're not in any condition\Nto help Dai or the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you're more likely\Nto drag them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't fight,\NI'll just serve as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use my body\Nto block the enemy attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy, where's my weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly. Where's my Dark Armour Spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't stand\Non the battlefield either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in having that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fight without your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So just accept it and get some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait Hyunckel! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy... You have feelings for Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, that didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll go even without a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All you did was take his weapon from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about him is beyond all reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why won't you give up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No human can be immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a normal human!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you were fully healed,\Nbut not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If it will help Dai and the others,\Nso be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... I've always been in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to watch anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To see you keep fighting hopeless battles\Nwhich leave you wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... stop walking gladly\Ninto death's arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do it gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The old me was a cursed Dark Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My guilt over turning my sword against\Nmy master and fellow students{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}continues to eat at my soul\Nand doesn't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It tears me apart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It terrifies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the pain and suffering\NI endure in deadly battle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,can alleviate my guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It tells me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm atoning for my sins\Nin the name of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hid it in the forest near the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend is calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never told anyone about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you're better off forgetting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bishop Fenbren!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember this one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense two sources of Orichalcum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The larger must be\NBaran's Demon Dragon Blade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it was the infamous Baran\Nwho scarred my face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the others had their wounds\Nhealed by Lord Hadorra,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I chose to leave my eyes as they were.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It cost me my eyesight,\Nbut I wanted to keep this wound...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to remind me of that humiliation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To keep the flames\Nof my vengeance burning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems not all of Hadorra's minions\Nare on the surface.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave this to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm that one's target.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you wish to waste the life\Nthat I spared, so be it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time I'll end things\Nwith a single swing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's strange.\NThis calmness can't be good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magic Power?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagikurosai!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Using Bagikurosai underwater?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though the spell could backfire?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Orichalcum left the life-signal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got you, Baran!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To defeat a powerful enemy like you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I figured I had to use my strongest attack\Nright from the start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Twin Sword Pinning!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I just target your life-signal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and hit you with this finishing attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The flow's changed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran... falls!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
